    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >进入自己中世纪村庄的统治者角色，从第一人称视角实时管理和发展它。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >保护村庄的中心——市政厅，不要让敌人摧毁它。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>收集和管理资源</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348440/extras/526a3a2dc3d96dc003b567e98a83e80c.poster.avif?t=1769266855\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348440/extras/526a3a2dc3d96dc003b567e98a83e80c.webm?t=1769266855\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348440/extras/526a3a2dc3d96dc003b567e98a83e80c.mp4?t=1769266855\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 提取5种资源。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 通过发展您的定居点获得黄金宝箱。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 在射箭工作坊中生产箭矢。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 寻找浆果丛为您的子民提供食物。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>发展和管理定居点</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348440/extras/0bcaf62360627a9a33ac25cbf94baa90.poster.avif?t=1769266855\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348440/extras/0bcaf62360627a9a33ac25cbf94baa90.webm?t=1769266855\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348440/extras/0bcaf62360627a9a33ac25cbf94baa90.mp4?t=1769266855\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 升级市政厅。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 建造8种建筑。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 通过管理面板管理您的定居点。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>探索</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348440/extras/95e6d90a037d87f39a13b147b01804f5.poster.avif?t=1769266855\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348440/extras/95e6d90a037d87f39a13b147b01804f5.webm?t=1769266855\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348440/extras/95e6d90a037d87f39a13b147b01804f5.mp4?t=1769266855\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 在地图上寻找资源。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 搜寻并采集或食用蘑菇。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 摧毁敌方营地。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 解放瞭望塔。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 控制矿井。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>招募和管理单位</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348440/extras/1db8dc02e3690c4d118b75cb0b5cc32e.poster.avif?t=1769266855\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348440/extras/1db8dc02e3690c4d118b75cb0b5cc32e.webm?t=1769266855\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348440/extras/1db8dc02e3690c4d118b75cb0b5cc32e.mp4?t=1769266855\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 招募7种单位。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 向您的单位发布命令。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 将单位排列成阵型。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>战斗</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348440/extras/6614d470f36c70775819fa29f95171b9.poster.avif?t=1769266855\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348440/extras/6614d470f36c70775819fa29f95171b9.webm?t=1769266855\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348440/extras/6614d470f36c70775819fa29f95171b9.mp4?t=1769266855\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 与您的士兵并肩作战。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 获得经验值并提升技能。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 使用剑和盾或弓箭。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 使用药水。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>创建升级和研究</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348440/extras/0fda72db93ba37136a2d665e01b7b493.poster.avif?t=1769266855\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348440/extras/0fda72db93ba37136a2d665e01b7b493.webm?t=1769266855\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348440/extras/0fda72db93ba37136a2d665e01b7b493.mp4?t=1769266855\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 升级建筑。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 为您自己和您的单位创建升级。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 进行研究。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>你准备好带领你的定居点走向荣耀并保护它免受所有威胁了吗？</strong></p>",
